verbose_text: All the images shown in XREF_FIG were taken 24 h after scratching and display the effect of the gene transfer for 3 different concentrations of AIVP (1 : 500,000, 1 : 50,000, and 1 : 5,000) depicted by GFP (green) on the iNOS expression shown using TRITC (red) with or without SM treatment.
